f","tid":340500,"uid":81308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>車仔麵好似唔係呢間喎 再行入少少 馬會隔離</blockquote><br />\n好細間舖舖仔 冇冷氣冇風扇 坐位都好少唔會舒適得去邊 但全沙田最好食既車仔麵係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個辣汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲好記得個時中學同2，3個fd去食<br />\n其中我同另一個fd叫左3個餸<br />\n其中2個餸分別係牛柏葉同豬腸<br />\n另一個就唔同<br />\n跟住返到屋企就不約而同一齊肚屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28244d79334b05931c76cf4fd040f2c36c402039","tid":340500,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>車仔麵好似唔係呢間喎 再行入少少 馬會隔離</blockquote><br />\n好細間舖舖仔 冇冷氣冇風扇 坐位都好少唔會舒適得去邊 但全沙田最好食既車仔麵係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個辣汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲好記得個時中學同2，3個fd去食<br />\n其中我同另一個fd叫左3個餸<br />\n其中2個餸分別係牛柏葉同豬腸<br />\n另一個就唔同<br />\n跟住返到屋企就不約而同一齊肚屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n車仔面既精髓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗱喳面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470332210a33a2bd13d2622d23c474049885eaac","tid":340500,"uid":14703,"like":0,"dislike